questions.question: Confirm the equipment with below provided image of the equipment
upload the image of the equipment, contact the technical team for recorrections and scan the bar code again
confirm is there any physical damage of the equipment
prepare the Incident / Damage and Missing report.
connect the equipment to the mains and check whether the equipment is getting ON
check whether the wall outlet is provided with AC Voltage of 230
shift the equipment to another place where wall outlet is provided with 230 AC Voltage
check the continuity of power cord and confirm whether the power cord id defective
replace the power cord with a new one
check the AC Fuse for continuity and confirm whether they are defective
replace the fuses with new one
check for any carbon formation or breakage of input connector
clean or replace the input pin connector accordingly
open the equipment as shown in the video, check whether the input 230Vac is available at the power supply.
check the continuity of switch and confirm whether the switch is defective
replace the switch with a new one
check for any loose cable connection / breakage of cable to the power supply board.
reseat / replace the cable accordingly
check whether the output 9VDC is available at the power supply board
repair / replace the power supply board accordingly
